Dialogue: 0,00:01:14.260,00:01:19.840,辉英,,0,0,0,,A bunch of lines, right? A bunch of not just the regular lines, a bunch of
Dialogue: 0,00:01:19.840,00:01:26.520,辉英,,0,0,0,,straight lines. Does it occur to you as non-obvious
