Dialogue: 0,00:01:56.520,00:02:01.760,辉英,,0,0,0,,we don't get a straight line. We get a line that actually turns, right? Two things
Dialogue: 0,00:02:01.760,00:02:07.320,辉英,,0,0,0,,hitting to each other and it turns. But on the smooth portion, you see all straight
