Dialogue: 0,00:02:37.440,00:02:46.880,辉英,,0,0,0,,said this is the wave speed and if f is only a function of u then df du is only a function of u
Dialogue: 0,00:02:46.880,00:02:55.740,辉英,,0,0,0,,that means the speed at which the wave propagates they are just a function of u
