Dialogue: 0,00:03:04.520,00:03:11.260,辉英,,0,0,0,,the wave then locally the solution value u doesn't change and therefore the speed doesn't change
Dialogue: 0,00:03:11.260,00:03:20.480,辉英,,0,0,0,,intuitively that's the answer right mathematically let's do a little bit a little bit of analysis
Dialogue: 0,00:03:20.480,00:03:25.740,辉英,,0,0,0,,so so if we look at the differential equation
