Dialogue: 0,00:03:26.240,00:03:26.460,辉英,,0,0,0,,okay
Dialogue: 0,00:03:26.480,00:03:35.740,辉英,,0,0,0,,what what we can do is we can write the solution u at a particular x plus
Dialogue: 0,00:03:35.740,00:03:48.220,辉英,,0,0,0,,plus or minus x plus yes x plus uh df so let's let's just do this x plus a ct so let's look at
Dialogue: 0,00:03:48.220,00:03:56.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,a function along the the value of the solution along a straight line
