Dialogue: 0,00:04:52.440,00:04:59.320,辉英,,0,0,0,,So basically, let me use x0 to be a distinguishing from this x.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:59.560,00:05:02.200,辉英,,0,0,0,,So this is x0, this is t equal to 0.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:02.860,00:05:07.920,辉英,,0,0,0,,So as t increases, x is going to increase by c times t.
