Dialogue: 0,00:07:40.380,00:07:43.880,辉英,,0,0,0,,or you can write it as x minus ct equal to constant.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:45.280,00:07:47.280,辉英,,0,0,0,,Either way is fine.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:48.880,00:07:51.580,辉英,,0,0,0,,I think maybe you are thinking about this, right?
