Dialogue: 0,00:07:58.380,00:07:59.380,辉英,,0,0,0,,All right, okay.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:59.380,00:08:01.380,辉英,,0,0,0,,So now, another question is,
Dialogue: 0,00:08:01.380,00:08:04.880,辉英,,0,0,0,,how does the slope of the line depend on the local solution?
Dialogue: 0,00:08:05.880,00:08:09.880,辉英,,0,0,0,,The slope of the line is the inverse of df du, right?
Dialogue: 0,00:08:11.380,00:08:15.380,辉英,,0,0,0,,So if I have a df du locally equal to 0, for example,
Dialogue: 0,00:08:15.880,00:08:17.380,辉英,,0,0,0,,what kind of line should I get?
Dialogue: 0,00:08:17.880,00:08:19.380,辉英,,0,0,0,,I get a vertical line, exactly.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:19.380,00:08:21.880,辉英,,0,0,0,,If df du is equal to 0, c is equal to 0.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:22.380,00:08:23.380,辉英,,0,0,0,,I get a vertical line.
