Dialogue: 0,00:08:31.380,00:08:33.380,辉英,,0,0,0,,I get a line that tilts towards your right.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:33.880,00:08:36.380,辉英,,0,0,0,,And again, let's look at the Berger's equation
Dialogue: 0,00:08:36.380,00:08:38.880,辉英,,0,0,0,,to see how does my df du depend on u.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:38.880,00:08:40.380,辉英,,0,0,0,,So Berger's equation,
Dialogue: 0,00:08:41.380,00:08:45.380,辉英,,0,0,0,,if f of u is equal to u squared over 2,
Dialogue: 0,00:08:45.880,00:08:49.380,辉英,,0,0,0,,df du is equal to u,
Dialogue: 0,00:08:49.380,00:08:50.380,辉英,,0,0,0,,then,
Dialogue: 0,00:08:50.380,00:08:51.380,辉英,,0,0,0,,u less than 0, c is equal to 0.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:52.380,00:08:57.380,辉英,,0,0,0,,I get negatively sloping contours.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:57.380,00:09:00.380,辉英,,0,0,0,,u equal to 0, I get vertical contours.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:00.380,00:09:04.380,辉英,,0,0,0,,u greater than 0, I get rightward tilting contours.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:04.380,00:09:07.380,辉英,,0,0,0,,Let's look at this to see if that's the case.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:07.380,00:09:08.380,辉英,,0,0,0,,Right, so,
Dialogue: 0,00:09:08.380,00:09:09.380,辉英,,0,0,0,,so,
Dialogue: 0,00:09:09.380,00:09:12.380,辉英,,0,0,0,,when u is positive, the color is u,
Dialogue: 0,00:09:12.380,00:09:14.380,辉英,,0,0,0,,I get right sloping contours.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:14.380,00:09:17.380,辉英,,0,0,0,,When u is negative, I get left sloping contours.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:18.380,00:09:20.380,辉英,,0,0,0,,And when u is almost 0,
Dialogue: 0,00:09:20.380,00:09:21.380,辉英,,0,0,0,,towards here and here,
Dialogue: 0,00:09:21.380,00:09:23.380,辉英,,0,0,0,,I get vertical contours.
Dialogue: 0,00:09:23.380,00:09:25.380,辉英,,0,0,0,,And the more negative I get,
